Les 1001 nuits;;1990;;NC;;Adventure,Comedy,Fantasy;;5.5;;Philippe de Broca;;Catherine Zeta-Jones,Gérard Jugnot,Stéphane Freiss,Thierry Lhermitte,Vittorio Gassman,Roger Carel,Marc Dudicourt,Georges Montillier,Alfredo Pea,Valérie Rojan,Eric Métayer,Joy Graham,Maurice Lane,Tim Holm,Raymond Aquilon,Florence Pelly,Farida Khelfa,Faycal Smaili;;The young, beautiful virgin Sheherazade (Catherine Zeta-Jones, in her film debut) embarks on an adventure through the legends of the 1001 nights. Aided by a genie living in 1990 London who watches her through his TV, she meets all the great heroes and kings, when she's not getting stripped completely naked, that is.;;https://www.imdb.com/title/tt0098961/